column3:
<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Wezetonyi has a potentially profitable proposal for you.
Search for anything that can be repurposed.
Deliver the silver necklace to Wezetonyi.
Hey, you're the one who was looking for Gulool Ja! Would you say that you're good at finding things, generally speaking?
In that case, you might do well as a reforger. Our job is to hunt for things that can be repurposed.
Care to give it a try? Take a look around Archeo Alexandria, and if you find anything of value, I'll see you duly compensated!
There are amazing discoveries to be had in Archeo Alexandria─<Emphasis>if</Emphasis> you know where to look. Find something useful, and you'll be rewarded for your efforts.
You dig through the mountain of debris, but find only shapeless planks of wood and nonfunctional electrope.
You examine the broken streetlamp, but it's already been harvested for parts. Evidently someone has beaten you to the punch.
As you patiently comb through the enshadowed wreckage, a gleam catches your eye, and you pull up a silver necklace!
It's unlikely you will find anything more of value here. Return to Wezetonyi and apprise him of your discovery.
Oh ho! See that engraving? That's the Alexandrian coat of arms. And just look at the shape! How old is this thing?
It must have belonged to someone who lived in the old city generations ago─in any case, an impressive find, especially for your first try!
You, my friend, would make an excellent reforger. Here, take this payment for a job well done!
